graph LR
    Feast[Feast Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required/Optional)
    Feast -->|container orchestration<br/>REQUIRED| K8s[Kubernetes 1.11.3+]
    Feast -.->|persistent storage<br/>OPTIONAL| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL]
    Feast -.->|online store<br/>OPTIONAL| Redis[Redis 7+]
    Feast -.->|object storage<br/>OPTIONAL| S3[S3 / GCS / Azure Blob]
    Feast -.->|cloud warehouse<br/>OPTIONAL| Snowflake[Snowflake]
    Feast -.->|TLS certs<br/>OPTIONAL| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Feast -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Feast -.->|authentication<br/>OPTIONAL| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
    Feast -.->|CA trust<br/>OPTIONAL| TrustedCA[Trusted CA Bundle]

    %% Integration Points (ODH Components)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI integration<br/>discovery| Feast
    DSP[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|training features| Feast
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -.->|feature access| Feast
    KServe[KServe] -.->|inference features| Feast

    %% External Systems
    Feast -.->|feature repo sync| Git[Git Repository]
    Feast -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    %% Consumer Applications
    MLApp[ML Applications] -->|online features<br/>HTTPS/443| Feast
    TrainingJobs[Training Jobs] -->|historical features<br/>HTTPS/443| Feast

